column1: Smalltalk version of Cassowary - random constraints & vars timing test.
Each row represents one test.   All times are in milliseconds.  Column labels are as follows:
nCns: number of constraints and variables
nSolvers: number of solvers for this test (we solve the same problem multiple times)
nResolves: number of times new edit values are provided
testNo: test number (since we will generally repeat the same test many times with different random numbers)
totalAddTime: total time to add all of the initial constraints (for all nSolvers solvers)
totalEditAddTime: time to add the two edit constraints to all nSolvers solvers
totalResolveTime: total time to re-solve nResolves * nSolvers times
totalEditDeleteTime: time to delete the two edit constraints from all nSolvers
editAddTime: add time per edit constraint
editDeleteTime: delete time per edit constraint
